      "description": "Number of compaction operations completed in the last hour.\n\nCompaction frequency depends on write workload:\n- High writes: More frequent compactions\n- Read-heavy: Fewer compactions\n- Zero compactions for extended time: May indicate idle database or stalled compaction",
