      "description": "Disk write operation latency percentiles. Shows how long it takes to write and sync data to disk.\n\nFor SSDs, typical expectations:\n- p50: <1ms\n- p95: <5ms\n- p99: <10ms (threshold line)\n\nWrite latencies may spike during:\n- Compaction operations\n- Checkpoint/snapshot creation\n- High write throughput periods",
      "fieldConfig": {
